00:07:40.360 --> 00:07:43.600

        THEY THEN START TO SELL THEIR
        STOCKS AS MUCH AS THEY CAN.
      

00:07:43.600 --> 00:07:45.860

        THEY'RE MOTIVATED BY FEAR.


